            <title>[HBASE-13868] Correct &quot;Disable automatic splitting&quot; section in HBase book</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-13868</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This recommendation is not correct for &lt;b&gt;IncreasingToUpperBoundRegionSplitPolicy&lt;/b&gt; (which is default now)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Disable Automatic Splitting&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To disable automatic splitting, set hbase.hregion.max.filesize to a very large value, such as 100 GB It is not recommended to set it to its absolute maximum value of Long.MAX_VALUE.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
</description>
